Java target which type of project give short exmaple.

Java is commonly used for:

| Project Type         | Short Example                                      |
| -------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Web Applications     | Online shopping website                            |
| Backend APIs         | REST API for a mobile app                          |
| Enterprise Software  | Banking system                                     |
| Cloud Services       | Microservice running on Kubernetes                 |
| Android Apps         | Expense tracker app                                |
| Big Data             | Processing logs with Apache Hadoop or Apache Spark |
| Financial Systems    | Trading platform order management                  |
| Desktop Applications | Simple inventory management tool                   |
| Developer Tools      | Build tools like Apache Maven                      |

Typical Java projects:

* E-commerce backend
* Banking application
* Inventory management system
* Employee management portal
* Trading/order management server
* Cloud microservices
* Android apps

Java is primarily used for **server-side, enterprise, cloud, web, and Android development**, rather than embedded systems.
